point of beginning; containing an area of TWENTY ONE THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED NINETY-NINE (21,299) SQUARE METERS, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and marked on the ground by P.L.S. Cyl. Cons. Mons. 15 x 60 cms.; bearing true; date of subdivision survey, April 22 to June 12, 1955.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 24th day of October, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and sixty-seven.

(SGD.) FERDINAND E. MARCOS President of the Philippines

By the President: (SGD.) RAFAEL M. SALAS Executive Secretary

